      "text": [
        " حُلَّنِي حَيْثُ حَبَسْتَنِي قَالَ «هُوَ حِلٌّ حَيْثُ حَبَسَهُ اَللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ قَالَ أَوْ لَمْ يَقُلْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2561 - Humran ibn A'yan asked Imam (as) about a person who says, \"Release me where You have restrained me.\"\nImam (as) said: \"He is released where Allah (swt), the Almighty, has restrained him, whether he says it or does not say it.\""
        ]
      }
